        <Parent_String>Coccoidea (superfamily) [300378924], Sternorrhyncha (suborder) [300378925], Homoptera (order) [300310492], Insecta (class) [300310470], Hexapoda (subphylum) [300310468], Arthropoda (phylum) [300265687], Animalia (kingdom) [300249395], Eukaryota (domain) [300265677], living organisms (entities) [300390503], Living Organisms (hierarchy name) [300265673], Agents Facet [300264089]</Parent_String>
